# API server (@workspace/api-server) — copy to `.env` and adjust.

# ── Required ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
PORT=5100          # port the Express server binds to (throws if unset)

# ── Optional ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# NODE_ENV=development
# LOG_LEVEL=info    # pino log level (fatal|error|warn|info|debug|trace)

# HubSpot: the contact form writes to HubSpot through Replit's connector proxy
# (@replit/connectors-sdk) — OAuth is injected by Replit, so there is NO token
# env var in app code. Running outside Replit requires adapting the proxy call
# in src/lib/hubspot.ts to your own HubSpot credentials.
